SETUP AND RUNNING

Step 1: Create the python environment needed to run the script
You have to create and activate a Python virtual environment to
properly run this code. To create the virtual environment,
activate it and install the requirements, you need to run:

python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
python3 -m pip install -r requirements.txt


Step 2: Make the OpenAI API Key Available in the environment.

export OPEN_AI_API_KEY=<the secret api key goes here>


Step 3: Run the script 

python3 callgpt.py 
